title: Sublime Text 3 (3083) Linux
description:
Sublime Text 3 (3083) Linux
===========================

This torrent only consists of the patched sublime text
 3 build 3083 executables  for x32 and x64 (the installers
 tar archives are not patched).

It contains the following files:

* sublime_text_3_build_3083_x32.tar.gz
* sublime_text_3_build_3083_x64.tar.gz
* sublime_text_patched
* sublime_text_patched_x64
* sublime_text_unpatched
* sublime_text_unpatched_x64
* info.txt
* Sublime-Text-3-3083-Linux--md5-list.chks

This is how you install sublime text 3:

- Extract 'sublime_text_3_build_3083_x64.tar.gz' (x64) or 'sublime_text_3_build_3083_x32.tar.gz' (x32)
- Copy 'sublime_text_patched_x64' (x64) or 'sublime_text_patched' (x32) as 'sublime_text' to the installation directory

You can check the files using md5sum like this:

$ md5sum -c ./Sublime-Text-3-3083-Linux--md5-list.chks

Or just compare the md5 checksums you generate from the
 downloaded files to these (same order as above):

* d1be10594fe7093b1b43a888a48c838f
* 5da998bea29f9ca02a60d2b3cfc46fea
* 9bca6c8b7dac35ced91be260a13c8e8a
* 867f5544c0f5c23eb9cdc0445c4dfd4d
